## Jenkins Pipeline Parallel 平行處理


### 將 parallel 語法設定在專案上
![](https://i.imgur.com/BYD3cvl.png)

> parallel  範例如下
```
node {

   stage('Git Clone') {
       echo "Git Clone OK"
   }
   stage('Nuget Restore') {
       echo "Nuget Restore OK"
   }
   stage('Msbuild') {
       echo "Msbuild OK"
   }

 parallel (
  "Push": {
    stage("Push Server") {
       echo "Push OK"
    }
  },
  "Scan Code": {
    stage("Scan Code") {
        echo " Scan Code OK"
    }
  }
 )
}
```

